title: Floxite Fl-10h 10x Hand Held 2-sided Mirror with Stand, Clear

title: Olay Regenerist Luminous Tone Perfecting Cream, 1.7 Ounce
description: Let your skin concerns fade away. Reveal your most pearlescent beautiful skin with Regenerist Luminous Tone Perfecting Cream. Over 8 weeks its formula with a brightening complex fades the look of dark spots age spots sun spots and discoloration  evening your overall skin tone. Experience bright beautiful healthy-looking skin every day with Olay Regenerist Luminous Tone Perfecting Cream.

title: Clear Scalp and Hair Intense Hydration Nourishing Shampoo, 12.9 Ounce
description: Resilient, beautiful hair starts with the right foundation. Clear scalp and hair has a dual-action formulation: a white stripe of deep hydrating treatment, and an aqua stripe infused with cactus extract. It deeply hydrates the scalp and leaves hair resilient and beautiful.
